"
" ==================================
" Mappings file
" ==================================
"
"
" -----------------------------------------------------------------------
" Normal mode mappings
" -----------------------------------------------------------------------
"
" ---- Navigation to split windows with Ctrl + H, J, K, L
nnoremap <C-J> <C-W><C-J>
nnoremap <C-K> <C-W><C-K>
nnoremap <C-L> <C-W><C-L>
nnoremap <C-H> <C-W><C-H>
"
" ---- Resizing of windows with arrow keys
nnoremap <Up>    :resize -2<CR>
nnoremap <Down>  :resize +2<CR>
nnoremap <Left>  :vertical resize -2<CR>
nnoremap <Right> :vertical resize +2<CR>
"
" ---- Clear search highlight with F2
nnoremap <silent> <F2> :nohl<CR>
"
" ---- Enable folding with the spacebar
nnoremap <space> za
"
" ---- Open terminal at below-right
"nnoremap <silent> <leader><C-T> :belowright terminal<cr>export PYTHONPATH=$PYTHONPATH:.<cr>clear<cr>
nnoremap <silent> <leader><C-T> :belowright terminal<CR>:call term_sendkeys(bufnr('%'), "export PYTHONPATH=$PYTHONPATH:.\nclear\n")<CR>
"
" ---- Mapping of Ctrl-q to use the Kwbd
nmap <C-Q> <Plug>Kwbd
"
" ---- Use <leader> fp to format Python code
nnoremap <silent> <leader>fp :Black<cr>:CocCommand pyright.organizeimports<cr>
"
" -----------------------------------------------------------------------
" Terminal mode mappings
" -----------------------------------------------------------------------
"
" ---- Make terminal as typical window with C-T
tnoremap <C-T> <C-W>N
"
" ---- Export PYTHONPATH
tnoremap <leader><C-E> export PYTHONPATH=$PYTHONPATH:.<cr>
"
" -----------------------------------------------------------------------
" Tagbar mapping
" -----------------------------------------------------------------------
"
nmap <silent> <leader><Tab> :TagbarToggle<CR>
"
" -----------------------------------------------------------------------
" Live preview mapping for NerdTree
" -----------------------------------------------------------------------
"
nnoremap <leader><space> :call NERDTreeLivePreview()<CR>
"
" -----------------------------------------------------------------------
" Toggling paste
" -----------------------------------------------------------------------
"
nnoremap <leader>p :set paste!<CR>
"
" EOF
